1. cmd + click on every required place and then write to every place in single stroke
<p>cmd d then again and again same for multiple selection</p>
<p>cmd shift l = same as below</p>
<p>cmd right arrow - to the end from right</p>
<p>ctrl shift w - to wrap text</p>
<p>ctrl cmd arrow to move wrapped items</p>
<p>cmd shift D  to duplicate wrapped items</p>
<p>cmd shift k  to remove wrapped items</p>
<p>cmd shift v  intelligent paste </p>
<p>cmd []/select and reallign to allign wrapped items</p>
